bern_train_station.title: Population density percent change in Bern Train Station
bern_train_station.description:
The percent change in population density in Bern Train Station observed that day compared the median value of this same day (e.g. Tuesday) between January 3rd, 2020 and February 6th, 2020.
Example: on Tuesday, February 11th we noticed a change of -6.11% in Bern Train Station which means a decrease of population density of 6.11% compared to the median value of Tuesdays between January 3rd, 2020 and February 6th, 2020.
